th expired stocks</title><p>Pakoyo Fadhiru Kamba et al. (594&#x02013;598) assess the downsides of pharmaceutical donations.</p></sec></sec><sec><title>Global </title><sec><title>Improving health of women, adolescents and children</title><p>Carlos Dora et al. (604&#x02013;607) argue that environmental health policies can impact health outcomes. </p></sec><sec><title>Vector control options</title><p>Steve W Lindsay et al. (606&#x02013;608) consider the spread of arboviruses and vector control measures.</p></sec></sec></body></article>